No. 617. Grand Trunk Western Railway Company et al., Petitioners, v. Chicago and Eastern Illinois Railroad Company. April 2, 1906. Mr. G. W. Kretzinger, Mr. Wells H. Blodgett, Mr. W. O. Johnson and Mr. Edgar A. Bancroft for petitioners. Mr. W. H. Lyford for respondent.

Petition for a Writ of cer-' tiorari to the United States Circuit Court of Appeals for the Seventh Circuit denied.
